@startuml
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor White
    BorderColor Black
    ArrowColor Black
    FontSize 14
}
hide empty description

[*] -> Listing_View
Listing_View -right-> Writing_Message : contact chosen
Listing_View --> Error_State : listing unavailable

Writing_Message : entry/ open chat interface
Writing_Message -right-> Validating : send clicked
Validating -left-> Writing_Message : invalid message

Validating -down-> Message_Sent : message delivered
Validating -right-> Error_State : contact failed

Message_Sent -right-> [*] : confirmation shown
Error_State -down-> [*] : use case ends
@enduml
